Since 2009, Dr Biden has worked as a professor of English at Northern Virginia Community College over and above a sterling record of community work, including the Biden Health Initiative and Book Buddies program. Dr Jill Tracy Biden is a highly accomplished woman. She holds a Doctor of Education (Ed. D) in educational leadership from the University of Delaware and two master’s degrees:  Master of Education from West Chester State College and Master of Arts in English from Villanova University.
Since 2009, Dr Biden has worked as a professor of English at Northern Virginia Community College over and above a sterling record of community work, including the Biden Health Initiative and Book Buddies program. On top of the massive professional accomplishments, she is America’s incoming First Lady.



